  <!-- ===================================================================
       OWASP-SUPP-011: CVE-2025-15104 — "validator:validator" CPE collision
       (commons-validator, hibernate-validator, json-schema-validator,
        quarkus-hibernate-validator, smallrye-config-validator)
       =================================================================== -->
  <!--
    CVE-2025-15104 is an SSRF / restriction-bypass in the Nu Html Checker
    (validator.nu / vnu — an HTML-validation *server* application). OWASP matches it
    via the broad cpe:2.3:a:validator:validator:* against every Java jar whose artifact
